    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shallow trays made to hold moveable type for hand-type setting. These are divided into compartments for each letter in a font of type, and typically are laid out with capitals to the right and lower-case characters to the left.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
